{
  "stem": "11290.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some of the best friends of my parents and grandparents were Gentiles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It all ended by force after 1933.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to boys' school for four years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was during the years of World War I, in which the school was manned by two teachers only.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody else was at war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in 1919-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] 1919-- I entered the gymnasium, which was a nine year school that's preparatory to the university.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And there-- also, there were quite a few Jewish boys in the gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were good friends with all of them, with all kids in school and all the boys.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And later on, we were practically grownups when we left the school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were all good friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In fact, we belonged to the same fraternity.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had a fraternity in the last year, which was called Abituria--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1928.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And even at that time we were just Jews and Gentiles together singing student songs and in a way playing Alt Heidelberg, in our way-- drinking beer and having a good time.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were some, but they were minor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were some remarks where some teachers made perhaps remarks about [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] anti-Semitic remarks of some kind or another.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they elicited protests by the parents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Usually ended in apology.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was some time-- there was only actually one ridiculous incident that, while all the Jewish boys were out on Rosh Hashanah or Yom Kippur-- I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The other kids said, we're playing a trick on them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When they come back, we won't talk to them, because they were a little bit envious that it was that the Jewish boys had the days off.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that was all straightened out.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
